UML:UseCase.name: Create ticket from a running AAL Service

UML:TaggedValue.value: The TS can register a ticket based on the data sent by an AAL Service. It should be further specified if the communication is implemented directly by the reporting service or by the AAL Gateway.
The end user should be able to create a ticket via the web interface of the Ticketing system.

The end user will be able to send an e-mail to the TS operator and explain his/her request. As result the operator will register it as a new ticket on the behalf of the end user. If needed the operator may contact the end user and request more details about the request.
